流的业绩</a>。</p><p>此外，她还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-huge-summer-2025-shows-in-belfast-and-dublin-3814479">在贝尔法斯特和都柏林举办两场户外演出</a>，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">2025 年 Coachella 音乐节上</a>表演，除此之外，她还宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-us-brat-arena-tour-2025-buy-tickets-3815161">将于 4 月和 5 月进行美国舞台巡演</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/charli-xcx-tickets/artist/1638380?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=w5kS6WQlrxyKRHRTdeXVu1QiUkCSB7Uqx2Cb2s0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买剩余的门票。</p><p>她还将出演即将上映的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/charli-xcx-joins-new-film-alongside-jenna-ortega-and-natalie-portman-3822201"><em>《画廊主》</em></a>和<em>《牺牲》</em> 。近日， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/charli-xcx-has-given-her-verdict-on-2024s-biggest-films-3825111">Charli向粉丝们公开了传闻已久的Letterboxd账号，分享了她对今年上映电影的看法</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-shares-brat-manifesto-from-2023-we-must-cultivate-chaos-desire-and-destruction-3825246">Charli XCX 发布的 2023 年“小子”宣言：“我们必须培养混乱、欲望和破坏”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
韩国流行偶像在济州航空失事后表示哀悼并推迟活动https://www.nme.com/news/music/k-pop-idols-offer-condolences-postpone-activities-following-jeju-air-crash-3825233?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=k-pop-idols-推迟济州空难后的活动表示哀悼Carmen ChinMon, 30 Dec 2024 09:41:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3825233 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="韩流偶像哀悼推迟活动 韩国济州岛空难" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>韩国目前正在实行为期7天的哀悼期</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/k-pop-idols-offer-condolences-postpone-activities-following-jeju-air-crash-3825233">韩流偶像在济州航空失事后表示哀悼并推迟活动，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="韩流偶像哀悼推迟活动 韩国济州岛空难" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/k-pop-idols-condolences-postpone-activities-jeju-air-plane-crash-south-korea-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>鉴于最近在韩国务安发生的济州航空飞机失事事件，几位韩国流行歌手表示哀悼，并停止了预定的活动。</p><p> 12月29日，济州航空一架载有181人的飞机在务安国际机场降落时坠毁，仅剩两名机组人员幸存。 <a href="https://www.channelnewsasia.com/east-asia/south-korea-jeju-air-crash-bird-strike-boeing-737-800-what-happened-4830911">据官员称，这架飞机在最初尝试着陆时，控制塔首先收到鸟击警告。</a></p><p>几分钟后，飞行员发出了“求救”警告，然后再次尝试机腹着陆，起落架仍处于收起状态。飞机沿着跑道打滑，然后撞到跑道尽头的墙壁并起火。</p><p><a href="https://world.kbs.co.kr/service/news_view.htm?lang=e&amp;Seq_Code=190014">悲剧发生后，韩国代理总统崔尚木宣布全国哀悼期为 7 天</a>，哀悼期将持续到韩国标准时间 1 月 5 日午夜。为了纪念哀悼期，出于对遇难者的尊重，该国娱乐业取消了活动并发布节目。</p><p>几位韩国音乐家和名人在社交媒体上向灾难受害者的家人和亲人表示哀悼。 “我们向此次事故的遇难者及其家属表示最深切的哀悼。愿他们的灵魂安息。”12 月 29 日晚， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">SEVENTEEN</a>队长 S.Coups 在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEKpA7VzaNu/?hl=en">Instagram</a>上写道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a>成员兼独唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">Lisa</a>也宣布推迟直播并表示哀悼。 “我将不得不推迟这个月的直播。向所有受昨天韩国事故影响的家庭致以最深切的哀悼。”她写道。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/LISA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#丽莎</a>的<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1fae7.png" alt="🫧" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />更新</p><p>向济州航空7C2216航班悲剧的所有家人和朋友致以最深切和衷心的哀悼。 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f64f-1f3fb.png" alt="🙏🏻" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f90d.png" alt="🤍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/Z874UgP5HS">pic.twitter.com/Z874UgP5HS</a></p><p> — BLACKPINK BLINK UNION <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f495.png" alt="💕" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@BBU_BLACKPINK） <a href="https://twitter.com/BBU_BLACKPINK/status/1873569283311346044?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> 12月29日在福冈举行演唱会的韩国流行乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enhypen">ENHYPEN</a>也在演出中表达了敬意。 “我的心情很沉重，但我们将继续为今天来看我们的每个人尽力而为，”<a href="https://x.com/hannahyrax/status/1873252672247419224">队长 Jungwon 对人群说道</a>。</p><p>在韩国哀悼这场悲剧之际，一些影片的上映、促销和发布被取消或推迟。全国各地的许多新年庆祝活动都被取消，包括年度颁奖典礼、音乐节和音乐会。</p><p> <a href="https://x.com/pledis_17/status/1873277776683213217">BSS</a>和<a href="https://x.com/IVEstarship/status/1873301426497376682">IVE</a>等团体已暂时停止为即将发行的专辑进行预先安排的促销活动，但目前尚不清楚他们专辑的发行日期是否会受到影响。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/huh-yunjin">Huh Yunjin</a>也<a href="https://x.com/le_sserafim/status/1873587366159585322">推迟了原定于今天发行的即将发行的单曲“Jellyfish”的发行</a>。 <a href="https://x.com/Stray_Kids/status/1873308075748372681">Stray Kids 还暂停了</a>“SONG By”项目下一首新曲目的发行，两首歌曲的修订发行日期尚未公布。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">BTS</a>本周还将暂停 YouTube 系列节目<em><a href="https://x.com/bts_bighit/status/1873594919107149904">Run Jin</a></em>等内容<a href="https://x.com/bts_bighit/status/1873594919107149904">的发布</a>。</p><p>与此同时，众多艺人官方社交媒体渠道宣布，在哀悼期间不会上传社交媒体内容。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/exo">EXO 的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/baekhyun">伯贤</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/xiumin">Xiumin</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chen">Chen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-boyz">THE BOYZ</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/plave">PLAVE</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/viviz">VIVIZ</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shinee">SHINee 的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taemin">泰民</a>等。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/k-pop-idols-offer-condolences-postpone-activities-following-jeju-air-crash-3825233">韩流偶像在济州航空失事后表示哀悼并推迟活动，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
