w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-cast-of-Community-1068x675.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2272px) 100vw, 2272px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3580640" class="wp-caption-text"> 《社区》的演员阵容。图片来源：盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>“‘六季一部电影’一开始只是《社区》早期几季中的一句厚颜无耻的台词，但很快就为这部标志性、搞笑且酷炫的 NBC 喜剧点燃了一场热情的粉丝运动，”娱乐内容主席苏珊·罗夫纳 (Susan Rovner) 说道。 NBC环球电视和流媒体在一份声明中。</p><p> “我们非常感激 15 年后，我们能够向粉丝们交付这部承诺的电影，并且迫不及待地想与 Dan Harmon、Andrew Guest、Joel McHale、Sony 以及 UTV 的合作伙伴合作，继续这部史诗喜剧对于孔雀观众来说。”</p><p>今年早些时候，唐纳德·格洛弗（又名<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/childish-gambino">幼稚甘比诺</a>） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/donald-glover-provides-major-update-on-community-movie-3580609">确认他将回归出演<em>社区</em>电影</a>：“我全力以赴。” </p><figure id="attachment_3799847" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3799847" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3799847" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Donald-Glover.-CREDIT_-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3799847" class="wp-caption-text">唐纳德·格洛弗。图片来源：Christop