">分享</a>。</p><p>在不到 13 分钟的演出中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shaboozey">Shaboozey</a> 、Reyna Roberts、Tanner Adell、Brittney Spencer 和 Tiera Kennedy 等明星也加入了 Queen Bey 的行列。她的大女儿 Blue Ivy Carter 也加入了“Texas Hold &#39;Em”的舞蹈。</p><p>中场表演被球迷称为<a href="https://x.com/BobbyKingDeal/status/1872061642143650261" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“有史以来最好的超级碗表演，但它甚至不是超级碗”</a> ，为了拉开中场表演的序幕，碧昂丝表演了《16 马车》。她表演的其他歌曲包括《Blackbird》、《YA YA》、《My House》、《Jolene》等。 Shaboozey 与她一起拍摄了《Sweet Honey Buckiin》。</p><p>在其他地方，Post Malone 将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">亮相 2025 年 Coachella 音乐节</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3816795" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3816795" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3816795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live.jpg" alt="波斯特·马龙现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Post-Malone-performs-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3816795" class="wp-caption-text">波斯特·马龙在舞台上表演。图片来源：Astrida Valigorsky/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>该音乐节定于 4 月 11 日至 13 日和 4 月 18 日至 20 日举行，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-elliott">Missy Elliott</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>的表演、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">Lisa</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennie">Jennie</a> 、原版<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/misfits">Misfits</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">The Prodigy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fka-twigs">FKA Twigs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a>等的独奏表演。还有 XCX，其主导文化的 6 月发行版《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> 》<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">被评为年度专辑通过<i>NME</i></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-shares-heartwarming-message-to-beyonce-after-christmas-halftime-show-3825221">圣诞中场秀后，波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone) 向碧昂斯 (Beyoncé) 分享了感人肺腑的信息，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
